{"title":"Wolf Tooth adds Aero Chainguides for Cervelo, Otso Bikes","link":"https://bikerumor.com/wolf-tooth-adds-aero-chainguides-for-cervelo-otso-bikes/","date":1701014276000,"content":"<p><img width=\"2048\" height=\"1365\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/wolf-tooth-lonewolf-aero-chainguide-cervelo-road-bikes.jpg\" alt=\"wolf tooth LoneWolf aero chainguides on Team Jumbo-Visma cervelo road bikes\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/wolf-tooth-lonewolf-aero-chainguide-cervelo-road-bikes.jpg 2048w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/wolf-tooth-lonewolf-aero-chainguide-cervelo-road-bikes-297x198.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/wolf-tooth-lonewolf-aero-chainguide-cervelo-road-bikes-800x533.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/wolf-tooth-lonewolf-aero-chainguide-cervelo-road-bikes-120x80.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/wolf-tooth-lonewolf-aero-chainguide-cervelo-road-bikes-768x512.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/wolf-tooth-lonewolf-aero-chainguide-cervelo-road-bikes-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/wolf-tooth-lonewolf-aero-chainguide-cervelo-road-bikes-720x480.jpg 720w\" /></p>\n<p>Wolf Tooth Components <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wolf-tooth-lonewolf-aero-chainguide-corrals-your-1x-setup/\">got into the 1x chainguide game</a> this summer with universal options to fit most road and gravel bikes. Now, they’ve added model-specific units for Cervelo and Otso bikes.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/wolf-tooth-lonewolf-aero-chainguide-cervelo-bikes.jpg\"><img width=\"1187\" height=\"606\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/wolf-tooth-lonewolf-aero-chainguide-cervelo-bikes.jpg\" alt=\"wolf tooth lonewolf aero 1x chain guides for Cervelo road and gravel bikes\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/wolf-tooth-lonewolf-aero-chainguide-cervelo-bikes.jpg 1187w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/wolf-tooth-lonewolf-aero-chainguide-cervelo-bikes-297x152.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/wolf-tooth-lonewolf-aero-chainguide-cervelo-bikes-800x408.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/wolf-tooth-lonewolf-aero-chainguide-cervelo-bikes-120x61.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/wolf-tooth-lonewolf-aero-chainguide-cervelo-bikes-768x392.jpg 768w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Team Jumbo-Visma used the LoneWolf Aero Chainguide on their team bikes at Paris-Roubaix and Tour de France, and won with it at the Giro d’Italia and Unbound Gravel 2023. It’s specifically made for 1x drivetrains and allows 8mm of lateral adjustment without shims. The Cervelo models use a direct-mount, two-bolt design and come in Low-, Mid-, and High-Sweep designs to fit different chainring sizes on their road bikes, the R5CX cyclocross, and Aspero gravel bikes.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/wolf-tooth-lonewolf-aero-chainguide-otso-waheela-bikes.jpg\"><img width=\"610\" height=\"396\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/wolf-tooth-lonewolf-aero-chainguide-otso-waheela-bikes.jpg\" alt=\"wolf tooth LoneWolf aero 1x chain guide for Otso Waheela bike\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/wolf-tooth-lonewolf-aero-chainguide-otso-waheela-bikes.jpg 610w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/wolf-tooth-lonewolf-aero-chainguide-otso-waheela-bikes-297x193.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/wolf-tooth-lonewolf-aero-chainguide-otso-waheela-bikes-120x78.jpg 120w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>For the <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/otso-waheela-carbon-gravel-bike-gets-more-cargo-mounts-plus-four-new-colors/\">Otso Waheela C carbon gravel bike</a>, the LoneWolf Aero chainguides have an adjustable mounting slot with High- and Low-sweep designs, offering plenty of adjustment range. Both versions and all sizes retail for $39.95 each.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><em><a href=\"https://www.wolftoothcomponents.com/collections/chainguides\" target=\"_blank\">WolfToothComponents.com</a></em></p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wolf-tooth-adds-aero-chainguides-for-cervelo-otso-bikes/\">Wolf Tooth adds Aero Chainguides for Cervelo, Otso Bikes</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com\">Bikerumor</a>.</p>","author":"Tyler Benedict","siteTitle":"Bikerumor","siteHash":"49f427af0a926f4232eb837006841d7242e153e3afbb590f32e4b104ea3e2718","entryHash":"608b14ab68a5e890e65f49eb4bf3186f01af555ea81f6c1f255b46a4035d2336","category":"Cycling"}